A4.text: In 2022, Army defeated Navy by a score of 20–17 in double overtime in the first overtime game in the series' history.

A5.text: On December 10, 2016, Army defeated Navy for the first time since 2001 with a 21–17 victory, snapping its 14-game losing streak against Navy.
